dc_title_s: Algemeene kaart, der ontdekkingen van W. E. Parry en O. Von Kotzebue
dc_description_s: 1 map : hand col. ; 30 x 62 cm.|Relief shown with hachures.|Prime meridian: Greenwich.|General map of the discoveries of W. E. Parry and O. von Kotzebue, on their journeys in search of a north-westerly and north-east passage from the Atlantic to the Pacific from 1815 to 1820.|"Uit de Originele kaarten te zamengesteld en gegraveerd door C. van Baarsel & Zoon." The original maps composed and engraved by C. van Baarsel & Son.
